data.description: Paid off SOLAR! Discover desert paradise at its finest with this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home. This home has a brand new paid off solar system and next to no electric bill. Smart home and smart alarm system included. Nestled in a tranquil setting, this residence offers a spacious open-concept interior, modern kitchen amenities, and comfortable bedrooms. Step outside to a sprawling backyard, perfect for endless outdoor possibilities. Embrace the allure of Arizona living in this inviting home with ample space for both relaxation and entertainment.
